title: Nelly T’s Journey Through ‘The Challenge’ | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
The one, the only Nelly T, Nelson Thomas, joins Johnny this week to talk through his full journey from growing up in Inglewood, California, to being one of the most beloved competitors on ‘The Challenge’ and everything in between, including detours on Jerry Springer’s ‘Baggage on the Road,’ ‘Dr. Phil,’ and so much more.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Nelson Thomas
Producer: Sasha Ashall
